author: Caroline Kelly
title: Robert Redfield warns a second wave of the coronavirus this year could be worse because it will coincide with flu season
description: A second coronavirus outbreak could emerge this winter in conjunction with the flu season to make for an even more dire health crisis, the director of the Centers for Disease Control told The Washington Post in an interview.
